{"tid":1994692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為大佬任正非：美國永遠是朋友！","createTime":"2020-04-29T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T05:33:05.000Z","uid":57308,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"03bf9c0ddeea3f8f9dc87c37624be17afc7c4dd1","tid":1994692,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"華為創始人任正非與甘肅社科雜誌進行了交流。 在訪談中他被問到&ldquo;華為未來會將手機中的美國零部件都替換掉嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 對此，任正非回复，&ldquo;不會，美國永遠都是我們的好朋友。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 他提到，&ldquo;我們去年在美國採購了187億美元（約合人民幣1324億元）的零部件，過去只有110億美元，大幅增加了對美國零部件採購量。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 任正非進一步補充道，&ldquo;美國政府也批准了一些美國公司向我們供貨。美國少數政治家的提議不完全代表是美國政府的意見，很多美國公司得到美國商務部的批准向我們供應零部件，我們 沒有替換美國零部件的想法。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 此前對華為P40系列的拆解顯示，其主要元器件中僅射頻前端功放（PA）等少數元件來自美國廠商，比如高通、Skyworks、Qorvo等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vB6RhoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvB6RhoG.jpg&h=23b65ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗漢奸<br />\n對唔對得住14億中国人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69280ef34ebc639f64e4c8313870c4a2dc495550","tid":1994692,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40a8a32e12055425327ec8307f8bd48beacfe77","tid":1994692,"uid":57308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>賣國賊任正非<br />\n堅決控制漢奸企業華為</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11c3cc7f63bfa814c6cf27ecdc2f8c0327846c7","tid":1994692,"uid":155079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"無得做infrastructure 點賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔洗講佢個新eco system要幾多美國佬科技去開發"},{"pid":"6af1e4c0dbec4f492c2c0edc4fe6be831acf897f","tid":1994692,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/105003_d8c659fdefc467b1a2b89dea230830ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F105003_d8c659fdefc467b1a2b89dea230830ad.gif&h=2493eba5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25e6bf3174775c762a7edeb03e1ed0af31cdf33d","tid":1994692,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"中美冷戰<br />\n華為比美國全面封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6014e3d8842d8ff8db517497405904d7cd4d6db9","tid":1994692,"uid"